254	faceted	barrett's esophagus	Find the causes and risk factors of Barrett's Esophagus.	clueweb12-0201wb-28-25898	1	http://www.healthnewsflash.com/conditions/barretts_esophagus.php	<html> <!-- #BeginTemplate "/Templates/main.dwt" --> <head> <link href="/fonts.css" rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" /> <title>Barrett's Esophagus - Causes, Symptoms &amp; Treatment</title> <meta name="description" content="Barrett's Esophagus Facts plus the Latest News on Barrett's Esophagus Treatments - HealthNewsflash" /> <meta name="keywords" content="barrett's esophagus, esophagus, cancer, care, gerd, disease, health, treatment, heartburn, adenocarcinoma, barrett's, dysplasia, oncology, chemotherapy, hepatitis" /> <script language="JavaScript1.2" src="http://www.healthnewsflash.com/glossary.js" type="text/javascript"></script> </head> <body topmargin="0" leftmargin="0" marginwidth="0" marginheight="0" bgcolor="#FFFFFF"> <!--start header--> <table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0"> <tbody> <tr> <td align="left" width="300" colspan="3"><img border="0" width="300" height="105" src="/images/header_left.jpg" /></td> <td align="left" colspan="2"><a href="http://www.healthnewsflash.com/"><img src="/images/header_logo.jpg" border="0" alt="HealthNewsflash" /></a><img src="/images/transpix.gif" width="10" height="1" /></td> </tr> </tbody> </table> <table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0"> <tbody> <tr> <td align="left"><a href="/"><img border="0" src="/images/tab_home.jpg" /></a></td> <td align="left"><a href="/myhealth.php"><img border="0" src="/images/tab_myhealth.jpg" /></a></td> <td align="left"><a href="/archives.php"><img border="0" src="/images/tab_news.jpg" /></a></td> <td align="left"><a href="/conditiona2z.php"><img border="0" src="/images/tab_medical.jpg" /></a></td> </tr> </tbody> </table> <table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0"> <tbody> <tr> <td colspan="4"><img border="0" height="11" src="/images/regmid.jpg" /></td> <td width="100%" colspan="4"><img bo