ge as he quits centre stage after 50 years – Times Online&quot;</a>. <i>The Times</i> (London)<span class="printonly">. <a rel="nofollow" class="external free" href="http://www.timesonline.co.uk/tol/news/world/us_and_americas/article3399819.ece">http://www.timesonline.co.uk/tol/news/world/us_and_americas/article3399819.ece</a></span><span class="reference-accessdate">. Retrieved April 22, 2009</span>.</span><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.atitle=Fidel+Castro+bows+to+illness+and+age+as+he+quits+centre+stage+after+50+years+%E2%80%93+Times+Online&amp;rft.jtitle=The+Times&amp;rft.aulast=Catan&amp;rft.aufirst=Thomas&amp;rft.au=Catan%2C%26%2332%3BThomas&amp;rft.date=February+20%2C+2008&amp;rft.place=London&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.timesonline.co.uk%2Ftol%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fus_and_americas%2Farticle3399819.ece&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Fidel_Castro"><span style="display: none;">&nbsp;</span></span></span></li> <li id="cite_note-fade-out-369">^ <a href="#cite_ref-fade-out_369-0"><sup><i><b>a</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-fade-out_369-1"><sup><i><b>b</b></i></sup></a> <span class="reference-text"><span class="citation web"><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.washingtontimes.com/news/2008/feb/24/fidels-fade-out/">&quot;Fidel's fade-out&quot;</a><span class="printonly">. <a rel="nofollow" class="external free" href="http://www.washingtontimes.com/news/2008/feb/24/fidels-fade-out/">http://www.washingtontimes.com/news/2008/feb/24/fidels-fade-out/</a></span>.</span><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=bookitem&amp;rft.btitle=Fidel%27s+fade-out&amp;rft.atitle=&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.washingtontimes.com%2Fnews%2F2008%2Ffeb%2F24%2Ffidels-fade-out%2F&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Fidel_Castro"><span style="display: none;">&nbsp;</span></span></span></li> <li i