ev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=Fidel%3A+A+Biography+of+Fidel+Castro&amp;rft.aulast=Bourne&amp;rft.aufirst=Peter+G.&amp;rft.au=Bourne%2C%26%2332%3BPeter+G.&amp;rft.date=1986&amp;rft.place=New+York&amp;rft.pub=Dodd%2C+Mead+%26+Company&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Fidel_Castro"><span style="display: none;">&nbsp;</span></span></li> <li><span class="citation book" id="Cas86">Castro, Fidel; Elliot, Jeffrey M. and <a href="wiki-Mervyn_M._Dymally" title="Mervyn M. Dymally">Dymally, Mervyn M.</a> (interviewers) (1986). <i>Nothing Can Stop the Course of History</i>. New York: Pathfinder Press. <a href="wiki-International_Standard_Book_Number" title="International Standard Book Number">ISBN</a>&nbsp;<a href="wiki-Special:BookSources/0873486617" title="Special:BookSources/0873486617">0873486617</a>.</span><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=Nothing+Can+Stop+the+Course+of+History&amp;rft.aulast=Castro&amp;rft.aufirst=Fidel&amp;rft.au=Castro%2C%26%2332%3BFidel&amp;rft.date=1986&amp;rft.place=New+York&amp;rft.pub=Pathfinder+Press&amp;rft.isbn=0873486617&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Fidel_Castro"><span style="display: none;">&nbsp;</span></span></li> <li><span class="citation book" id="Cas09">Castro, Fidel; Ramonet, Ignacio (interviewer) (2009). <i>My Life: A Spoken Autobiography</i>. New York: Scribner. <a href="wiki-International_Standard_Book_Number" title="International Standard Book Number">ISBN</a>&nbsp;<a href="wiki-Special:BookSources/9781416562337" title="Special:BookSources/9781416562337">9781416562337</a>.</span><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=My+Life%3A+A+Spoken+Autobiography&amp;rft.aulast=Castro&amp;rft.aufirst=Fidel&amp;rft.au=Castro%2C%26%2332%3BFidel&amp;rft.date=2009&amp;rft.place=New+York&amp;rft.pub=Scribner&amp;rft.isbn=97814165623